Dr. Gene TD Upper Arm Bp Monitor Price: Rs.1525

Key Features

  • Pulse Rate Indicator
Dr Gene TD AccuSure BP Monitor offers you a fully automatic measurement process with consistent and accurate readings. With this BP monitor you could keep a regular check on your blood pressure in the comforts of your home.

This upper arm Dr Gene BP monitor features an Irregular Heartbeat Detection that identifies and alerts you of abnormal heartbeats while your pressure is being measured. This BP monitor has been regulated and approved by the department of Weights and Measures hence making it genuine and reliable.

Build

Ergonomically designed to meet comfort and ease of use this BP monitor is simple in its operation. The TD AccuSure BP monitor comes with two main components comprising of the main unit and a non-integrated cuff attachment. The main unit displays a large LCD screen that is capable of showing your readings in a digitized format.

The non-integrated cuff has been designed for easy-positioning. You can easily attach this cuff to your arm without much effort. All you have to do is wrap the cuff around your arm and press the control buttons to start the measuring process.

Performance

With the Comfort Inflation technology integrated in the BP monitor the device detects your blood pressure while the cuff is inflating thereby providing a quicker measurement time. This Dr Gene AccuSure BP monitor uses the Oscillometric method to determine your blood pressure. The upper arm BP Monitor comes with an in-built sensor that allows automatic inflation and deflation thus leading to precise measurement readings.

The TD AccuSure BP monitor by Dr Gene is capable of displaying a range from 0-300 mmHg for pressure readings and 40-199 beats/min for pulse rates. Bestowed with a Memory feature this upper arm digital BP monitor can store 100 sets of measurement readings with date and time. This automatic memory function also allows four people to save their BP readings to track over time. The measurement accuracy of the monitor is calibrated at +/-3 mmHg for pressure readings and +/-4% of reading for pulse progress. This BP monitor is powered by 4 AAA batteries. You also have the option of using electricity as an alternate power source (Adapters to be bought separately).
